column2: - This is a publically editable sheet, please leave the master sheet alone for others to use.
column16: Stats for Mondays Games should be up here after they are posted on ocua.ca

column2: - Collaborate as much as possible (in sheet chat is built in at the top right, only accessible if you sign in to Google.)
- It is expected that you create your own sheet (in this worksheet) for eveyone to enjoy.
- Duplicate the master sheet, and RENAME it, "Copy of Week 1 - MASTER ...." or "Sheet1" are not cool names.
- Respect the work of others, no sabotaging others stats.
- This is a public space, anything you have in here you should be comfortable saying(showing) at the games.
- Don't use your stats for evil.
